You've entered a backyard.

You hear a noise behind you and spin around, but you can't see anything other than a patio table. I guess it's true what they say, if you're looking for a patio table, go to TextWorld. But oh no! there's nothing on this piece of garbage. You hear a noise behind you and spin around, but you can't see anything other than a patio chair. The patio chair is stylish. But the thing is empty, unfortunately. Aw, here you were, all excited for there to be things on it! You can make out a closed BBQ, which looks recent, nearby.

There is an open wooden door leading east. There is an open patio door leading west. There is an exit to the south.
